# Kurate Design System Rules

You are working in the Kurate web app. This project uses Tailwind CSS v4 with a custom design token system.

## CRITICAL: Never Use These

- ❌ Hardcoded hex values in className: `bg-[#1A5C4B]`, `text-[#F5F0E8]`
- ❌ Tailwind default colors: `bg-blue-500`, `text-gray-600`, `border-slate-200`
- ❌ Raw px in className for font sizes: `text-[14px]`, `text-[48px]`
- ❌ Inline style for visuals: `style={{ color: "#...", boxShadow: "...", fontSize: "..." }}`
- ❌ Default Tailwind radii: `rounded-2xl`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-3xl`
- ❌ Arbitrary container widths: `max-w-[800px]`, `max-w-[1280px]`
- ❌ Arbitrary box shadows: `shadow-[0_4px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]`

## Colors — Always Use Semantic or Brand Tokens

### Semantic (for all UI components)

- `bg-background` / `text-foreground` — page/body
- `bg-primary` / `text-primary-foreground` — primary actions
- `bg-secondary` / `text-secondary-foreground` — secondary surfaces
- `bg-muted` / `text-muted-foreground` — disabled/subtle
- `bg-card` / `text-card-foreground` — cards (white surface)
- `bg-destructive` / `text-destructive-foreground` — errors
- `border-border` — all borders
- `ring-ring` — focus rings

### State Colors (for status indicators)

- success: `bg-success-bg text-success-foreground`
- warning: `bg-warning-bg text-warning-foreground`
- info: `bg-info-bg text-info-foreground`

### Brand (for brand moments only — landing page, logo areas)

- `bg-cream`, `bg-ink`, `bg-teal`, `bg-lavender`, `bg-lavender-dark`, `bg-amber`, `bg-amber-dark`

### Opacity

Use Tailwind's opacity modifier: `text-ink/60`, `bg-teal/10`, `border-ink/[0.06]`

## Border Radius — Use Named Tokens Only

| Component     | Class           |
|--------------|-----------------|
| Button       | rounded-button  |
| Card         | rounded-card    |
| Input        | rounded-input   |
| Badge/tag/chip | rounded-badge |
| Full pill    | rounded-pill    |

## Shadows — Use Shadow Scale

`shadow-xs` → `shadow-sm` → `shadow-md` → `shadow-lg` → `shadow-xl` → `shadow-inner`

Cards use `shadow-sm` at rest, `shadow-md` on hover.

## Typography

- **Font families:** font-sans (body), font-serif (headlines only), font-mono (metadata/code)
- **Sizes:** text-xs text-sm text-base text-lg text-xl text-2xl text-3xl text-4xl text-5xl text-6xl text-7xl

## Layout Containers

- `container-page` — max-width 1280px, centered, with horizontal padding
- `container-content` — max-width 800px, for readable prose/articles

## Component Variants

Always use CVA. Shared base variants are in src/lib/variants.ts:

- buttonVariants — 5 variants × 4 sizes
- badgeVariants — 5 variants
- inputVariants — base input style

```tsx
import { buttonVariants } from "@/lib/variants";
import { cn } from "@/app/_libs/utils/cn";

<button className={cn(buttonVariants({ variant: "primary", size: "md" }), className)} />
```

## Animation

Use Framer Motion spring presets from src/app/_libs/utils/motion.ts:

- springSnappy — tab indicators, quick reveals
- springGentle — most UI transitions
- springBouncy — playful elements
- springHeavy — panels, page entry

Never use CSS ease-in-out, linear, or transition-all alone.

